# Mac环境用Docker部署EFK

## 安装docker
用brew进行安装
```
brew install docker
```

## 安装部署elasticsearch
1. 拉取elasticsearch镜像
   ``` 
   docker pull elasticsearch:6.8.0
   ```
2. 部署elasticsearch镜像
   ``` 
   docker run -e ES_JAVA_OPTS="-Xms256m -Xmx256m" -d -p 9200:9200 --name es-master elasticsearch:6.8.0
   ```
3. 验证是否部署成功，访问http://localhost:9200/
   ![avatar](data:image/png;base64,)

## 安装部署kibana
1. 拉取kibana镜像
   ```
   docker pull kibana:6.8.0
   ```
2. 部署kibana镜像
   ```
   docker run --link es-master:elasticsearch -p 5601:5601 --name kibana -d kibana:6.8.0
   ```
3. 验证是否部署成功，访问地址http://localhost:5601/
   ![avatar](data:image/png;base64,)

## 配置spring boot 应用
1. 修改application.yml
   ```yml
   logging:
      path: /Users/jingxuan/log
   spring:
      application: demo
2. 修改logback配置文件
   ```xml
   <appender name="logFile"
              class="ch.qos.logback.core.rolling.RollingFileAppender">
        <file>${logging.path}/${application.name}.log</file>
        <rollingPolicy class="ch.qos.logback.core.rolling.TimeBasedRollingPolicy">
            <fileNamePattern>${logging.path}/${application.name}/info-%d{yyyy-MM-dd_HH}.%i.log</fileNamePattern>
            <timeBasedFileNamingAndTriggeringPolicy
                    class="ch.qos.logback.core.rolling.SizeAndTimeBasedFNATP">
                <maxFileSize>100MB</maxFileSize>
            </timeBasedFileNamingAndTriggeringPolicy>
        </rollingPolicy>
        <encoder charset="UTF-8">
            <pattern>${logging.pattern.file}</pattern>
        </encoder>
    </appender>
## 本地安装部署Filebeat
1. 本地brew安装filebeat
   ```
   brew install filebeat
   ```
2. 更改filebeat配置
   ```
   vi /usr/local/etc/filebeat/filebeat.yml
   ```
   配置如下：
   ```yml
   filebeat.inputs:
   - type: log
   paths:
      - /Users/jingxuan/log/demo/*.log
   output.elasticsearch:
      hosts: ["localhost:9200"]
   setup.kibana:
      host: "localhost:5601"
  
3. 启动filebeat应用
   ```
   filebeat run
   ```
